OL,4,Chammer attack trial
OL,6,FA jury has begun its deliberations in
OL,7,Fthe trial of a public schoolboy
OL,8,Faccused of attacking two sleeping
OL,9,Fstudents and a teacher with hammers at
OL,10,Fa boarding school.
OL,12,FThe 16-year-old, who cannot be named
OL,13,Ffor legal reasons, is accused of three
OL,14,Fcounts of attempted murder in
OL,15,Fconnection with the incident at
OL,16,FBlundell's School in Tiverton, Devon,
OL,17,Fin June last year.
