OL,4,Chammer attack trial
OL,6,FDuring the two-month trial, Exeter
OL,7,FCrown Court heard the boy was wearing
OL,8,Fjust his boxer shorts and was "on a
OL,9,Fmission" to protect himself from a
OL,10,Fzombie apocalypse when he carried out
OL,11,Fthe attack.
OL,13,FThe teenager claimed he was
OL,14,Fsleepwalking when he assaulted the two
OL,15,Fboys and housemaster Henry Roffe-
OL,16,FSilvester.
OL,18,FThe boy is accused of arming himself
OL,19,Fwith three claw hammers and waiting
OL,20,Ffor the two boys to be asleep before
OL,21,Fattacking them.
