OL,4,Chammer attack trial
OL,6,FBoth boys suffered skull fractures, as
OL,7,Fwell as injuries to their ribs,
OL,8,Fspleen, a punctured lung and internal
OL,9,Fbleeding.
OL,11,FMr Roffe-Silvester suffered six blows
OL,12,Fto his head.
OL,14,FThe defendant, now aged 17, accepts
OL,15,Fcarrying out the attacks but says he
OL,16,Fis not guilty of three charges of
OL,17,Fattempted murder because he was
OL,18,Fsleepwalking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
