OL,4,Chammer attack trial
OL,6,FHe told the jury he had no
OL,7,Frecollection of the attacks and
OL,8,Fremembers falling asleep on the
OL,9,Fevening of June 8 and then seeing the
OL,10,Froom covered in blood.
OL,12,F"I remember being in the room. The
OL,13,Froom was covered in blood. What I
OL,14,Fcould see was blood. I didn't hear
OL,15,Fanything," he told the court.
OL,17,F"I remember walking out to the
OL,18,Fcorridor."
