OL,6,FHe added: "I knew something really bad
OL,7,Fhad gone on and everyone was looking
OL,8,Ftowards me.
OL,10,F"I didn't remember doing anything so
OL,11,Fthe only rational thing I was thinking
OL,12,Fwas that I was sleepwalking."
OL,14,FThe boy told the court he kept two
OL,15,Fhammers by his bed "for protection"
OL,16,Ffrom the "zombie apocalypse".
OL,18,FHe also had a screwdriver and a Swiss
OL,19,Farmy knife in his room.
