OL,6,FAsked to explain what a zombie
OL,7,Fapocalypse was, the boy said: "The end
OL,8,Fof the world."
OL,10,FThe boy said he did not intend to kill
OL,11,Feither Mr Roffe-Silvester or the two
OL,12,Fboys.
OL,14,F"I feel very terribly sorry for all
OL,15,Fthree individuals because of what I
OL,16,Fdid to them. I feel very sorry for
OL,17,Feveryone, the families and
OL,18,Fthemselves," he said.
