OL,6,FInviting the jurors to begin their
OL,7,Fdeliberations, trial judge Mrs Justice
OL,8,FCutts told them they were under no
OL,9,Fpressure of time.
OL,11,F"It is important you try and reach
OL,12,Fverdicts that are unanimous ` that
OL,13,Fmeans verdicts on which you all
OL,14,Fagree," she said.
OL,16,F"The law permits me in certain
OL,17,Fcircumstances to accept verdicts that
OL,18,Fare not verdicts of you all.
