OL,6,F"Those circumstances have not yet
OL,7,Farisen, so when you retire, I ask you
OL,8,Fto reach verdicts upon which each one
OL,9,Fof you is agreed.
OL,11,F"Should the time (come) when I can
OL,12,Faccept majority verdicts, I will call
OL,13,Fyou back into court to give you
OL,14,Ffurther directions.
OL,16,F"Please feel under no pressure of
OL,17,Ftime."
OL,19,FThe jury will resume its deliberations
OL,20,Fon Tuesday.
